.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-FEE-PPM-AVG" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-fee-ppm-avg \- FEAT-2361 average fee PPM for settled forwards
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-fee-ppm-avg
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the average fee in parts-per-million (fee_msat*1e6/in_msat) across all settled forwards (FEAT-2361).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
